      <h2 class="h4 mb-8 h2-sm">The XRP Ledger: A Scalable, Sustainable Blockchain</h2>
      <h6 class="longform mb-10">The XRP Ledger (XRPL) is a decentralized, public blockchain led by a global developer community.</h6>
      <p class="mb-0">It’s fast, energy efficient, and reliable. With ease of development, low transaction costs, and a knowledgeable community, it provides developers with a strong open-source foundation for executing on the most demanding projects—without hurting the environment.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-new py-26">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column-reverse col-sm-8 p-0">
      <h3 class="h4 h2-sm">Why developers choose the XRP Ledger</h3>

    </div>
    <ul class="mt-10 card-grid card-grid-3xN" id="benefits-list">
      <li class="col ls-none">
        <img id="public" alt="Public and Decentralized Structure Icon">
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Public and Decentralized Structure</h4>

      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none">
        <img id="streamlined" alt="Streamlined <br class='until-sm'/>Development Icon">
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Streamlined <br class="until-sm">Development</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">Tools and documentation that speed development and reduce time to market</p>
      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none">
        <img id="performance" alt="High <br class='until-sm'/>Performance Icon">
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">High <br class="until-sm">Performance</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">Capable of settling thousands of transactions in seconds</p>
      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none">
        <img id="low-cost" alt="Low Cost Icon">
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Low Cost</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">At fractions of a penny per transaction, costs are inexpensive enough to enable a wide variety of use cases</p>
      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none">
        <img id="community" alt="Vibrant Community Icon">
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Vibrant Community</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">Developers, validators, users, and businesses make the XRP Ledger better every day</p>
      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none">
        <img id="reliability" alt="Proven Reliability Icon">
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Proven Reliability</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">8+ years of consistent performance over more than 63 million ledgers</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container-new py-26">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column-reverse col-sm-8 p-0">
      <h3 class="h4 h2-sm">Activate the power of the XRP Ledger and find the building blocks for your next innovation</h3>

  <section class="container-new py-26">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column-reverse col-sm-8 p-0">
      <h3 class="h4 h2-sm">Explore what the community is building to enable new features and use cases on XRPL</h3>
      <h6 class="eyebrow mb-3">Preview New Features</h6>
    </div>
    <ul class="mt-10 card-grid card-grid-3xN">
      <li class="col ls-none pt-2">
        <a class="label chip-green" href="https://hooks-testnet.xrpl-labs.com/">In Development</a>
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Smart Contracts</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">Hooks are small, efficient WebAssembly modules designed specifically for the XRPL. Check out the <a href="https://hooks-testnet.xrpl-labs.com/" target="_blank">hooks amendment and public testnet</a> that enable smart contract functionality.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none pt-2">
        <a class="label chip-green" href="https://xrpl.org/docs.html#docs-hot-topic">In Development</a>
        <h4 class="mt-3 mb-0 h5">Non-Fungible Tokens</h4>
        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">Lower fees, faster transactions, and custom token functionality make the XRPL ideally suited for building an ecosystem for NFTs. Explore <a href="https://xrpl.org/docs.html#docs-hot-topic">proposed standards</a> for issuing NFTs.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="col ls-none pt-2">
        <a class="label chip-green" href="https://dev.to/ripplexdev/a-vision-for-federated-sidechains-on-the-xrp-ledger-2o7o">In Development</a>

        <p class="mt-6-until-sm mt-3 mb-0">Extend, experiment, and specialize a custom sidechain based on the XRPL's proven blockchain technology. Learn more about <a href="https://dev.to/ripplexdev/a-vision-for-federated-sidechains-on-the-xrp-ledger-2o7o" target="_blank">the vision of sidechains</a>.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>

html.light .page-uses #raisedinspace .biz-logo { content: url("../img/uses/lightmode/raised.png"); }

html.light .page-uses #towo .biz-logo { content: url("../img/uses/lightmode/towo.png"); }

html.light .landing-bg { opacity: 0.4; }

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  html.light .landing-bg { opacity: 1; }
}

html.light .landing-builtin-bg::before { opacity: 0.4; }

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  html.light .landing-builtin-bg::before { opacity: 1; }
}

html.light #feedback-content .docked-widget .widget-header { background-color: rgb(245, 245, 247) !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; }

html.light #feedback-content .docked-widget .widget-header-icon { filter: invert(100%); }

html.light .page-docs-index #software-and-sdks .card-deck .card:nth-child(2) .card-footer { background-image: url("../img/cards/lightmode/4col-light-blue.svg"); }

html.light .page-docs-index #doc-types .card-deck .card:nth-child(4) .card-footer { background-image: url("../img/cards/lightmode/4col-light-blue-2.svg"); }

html.light #find-us-on-platforms .card-deck .card:nth-child(2) .card-footer { background-image: url("../img/cards/lightmode/4col-light-blue-3.svg"); }

html.light .page-references #refs-types .card-deck .card:nth-child(2) .card-footer { background-image: url("../img/cards/lightmode/3col-green-2.svg"); }

html.light .page-references #xrpl-protocol .card-deck .card:nth-child(1) .card-footer { background-image: url("../img/cards/lightmode/4col-light-blue-4.svg"); }
